The Efficiency Expert;;1991;;PG;;Comedy,Drama;;6.2;;Mark Joffe;;Anthony Hopkins,Ben Mendelsohn,Alwyn Kurts,Bruno Lawrence,John Walton,Rebecca Rigg,Toni Collette,Russell Crowe,Angela Punch McGregor,Dan Wyllie,John Flaus,Gary Adams,Jeff Truman,Toni Lamond,Jillian Murray,Jacob Kino,Rosie Sturgess,Nathan Croft;;Errol Wallace (Sir Anthony Hopkins) is an efficiency expert, managing the high-profile downsizing of a major auto parts factory. But when he is hired to evaluate a small moccasin factory which seems to be from another era, Errol has to reconsider the rapid modernization he advocates, as he is confronted by the human faces such plans hurt.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0102969/